<!doctype html>
<html><head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>Legal Notice</title>
<style>
 @page { size: A4; margin: 20mm; }
 body { font-family: "Noto Sans", "Noto Sans Devanagari", sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.55; }
 .footer { font-size: 9pt; color: #555; border-top: 1px solid #ccc; margin-top: 24pt; padding-top: 8pt; }
 .bold { font-weight: 600; }
</style>
</head><body>

<p style="text-align: right;">Date: {{ slots.date }}</p>

<p>To,<br>
<span class="bold">{{ slots.recipient_name }}</span><br>
{{ slots.recipient_address }}</p>

<p><span class="bold">Subject:</span> {{ slots.subject }}</p>

<p>Dear Sir/Madam,</p>

<p>Under instructions from my client, <span class="bold">{{ slots.sender_name }}</span>
(hereinafter "my Client"), resident of {{ slots.sender_address }},
I hereby serve you with this legal notice on the following grounds:</p>

<p>{{ slots.facts }}</p>

<p>In view of the above, my Client hereby calls upon you to:</p>
<ol>
{% for demand in slots.demands %}
  <li>{{ demand }}</li>
{% endfor %}
</ol>

<p>Please treat this notice as final. Failing compliance within
{{ slots.response_window_days }} days from receipt, my Client shall be constrained
to initiate appropriate civil and/or criminal proceedings at your risk as to
cost and consequence.</p>

<p>Yours sincerely,<br>
{{ slots.sender_name }}</p>

<div class="footer">
  Drafted with NyayaSathi — an AI legal-information and document-drafting service.
  This document is not legal advice. For advice, consult a licensed advocate.
  {% if slots.call_uuid %}<br>Call Ref: {{ slots.call_uuid }}{% endif %}
</div>

</body></html>
